<postlude component="profesor"> 

  <!-- Posibles errores -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="errores-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students' diagrams indicate that they know which fraction is greater, but the symbol in the expression doesn't match their visual representation.</p>
  </paragraphs>


  <!-- Estrategia de apoyo si muchos estudiantes respondieron incorrectamente -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="apoyo-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Before the next day's warm-up, have students recap the important points of the previous lesson, specifically the meaning of the symbols <m>&lt;</m> and <m>&gt;</m>.</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

</project>